messages.content: ComfyUI Pronodes is a collection of utility nodes for ComfyUI that is still in development.
How can you install ComfyUI Pronodes?
ComfyUI Pronodes can be installed via the ComfyUI-Manager.
What does the Load Youtube Video node do?

The Load Youtube Video node downloads a video from a YouTube URL, saves it to the /output directory, automatically skips download if the video already exists locally, and displays the video and other details at the bottom of the node.
Which node allows for seamless integration with ComfyUI-VideoHelperSuite?
The Load Youtube Video node allows for seamless integration with ComfyUI-VideoHelperSuite.
What does the Preview VHS Audio node do?
The Preview VHS Audio node displays audio from ComfyUI-VideoHelperSuite.
What does the VHS Filenames to Path node do?
The VHS Filenames to Path node converts filenames to file paths from ComfyUI-VideoHelperSuite.
When was the Preview VHS Audio node and VHS Filenames to Path node added to ComfyUI Pronodes?
The Preview VHS Audio node and VHS Filenames to Path node were added to ComfyUI Pronodes on 08/03/2024.
